# --- build artifacts & deps (reconstructed by scripts/build-web.sh) ---
web/
**/node_modules/
**/build/
**/DerivedData/
**/.build/

# --- packaged outputs ---
/out/
*.ipa
*.xcarchive
*.dSYM.zip

# --- generated Xcode project (produced by XcodeGen from app/project.yml) ---
app/*.xcodeproj

# --- reference IPAs (Stremio's proprietary binaries, never commit) ---
reference/

# --- vendored nodejs-mobile (downloaded by scripts; ~51MB) ---
app/Vendor/

# --- bundled streaming server (extracted from Stremio's macOS app; proprietary) ---
app/Resources/server.js

# --- standalone node binary for the macOS streaming server (downloaded by
#     scripts/fetch-node-macos.sh; ~95MB; nodejs-mobile has no macOS slice) ---
app/Resources/node-darwin-arm64

# --- tooling / misc ---
.DS_Store
.playwright-mcp/
*.log

# agent / editor config
.claude/
app/Resources/fonts/
graphify-out/

# Internal working docs (planning, handoff, audits, design/product context).
# Kept locally for our own use; never published to the repo.
/HANDOFF.md
/PRODUCT.md
/DESIGN.md
/docs/PLAN.md
/docs/FEATURE-PARITY.md
/docs/0.3.0-PRD.md
/docs/REVIEW-WORKLIST.md
/docs/PLATFORM-ACQUISITION.md
/docs/PLAYER-CONTROLS-DEBUG.md
/docs/REBASE-iOS.md
/docs/REBASE-stremio-core.md
/docs/superpowers/
